- cs.GR (Graphics) is another possible category as the paper deals with image processing and calibration. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is a possible category as the paper deals with making computer vision algorithms more accessible to novice users. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with retrieving and aggregating calibration data.
